Text: The names of the people the Doctor thanks in the Forward seem to have a certain (uploader-edited?) "tongue-in-cheek" quality about them, such as "Heidi Hough" or "Ryan Greendyk", but the information that I've read seems valid, so far.
Thank you so much, now I will be able to help many more people with diabetes, thank you so much!
Thanks to all seeders and to uploader. Griff.
